-------- Documentation for dsmti version 2.2 --------

**********  Welcome to the DSM world.  **********

This is a package for full computations of  3-component
synthetic seismograms for a spherically symmetric TI
(transversely isoropic) earth model using the Direct
Solution Method.


CONFIGURATION:
        After editing environment variables in 'Makefile', type
	% make

USAGE:
	% dsmti < (parameter filename)

See 'USAGE' for details.

If you have any questions, requests or complaints, please feel
free to contact to
  takeuchi@eri.u-tokyo.ac.jp


						Nozomu Takeuchi
